t=0
draw=_=>{t||createCanvas(W=720,W)
t+=.05
colorMode(HSB)
noStroke()
background(0)
for(y=0;y<W;y+=89)for(x=0;x<W;x+=2)fill(y/2,70+(S=sin(R=x/17*PI+t*4)*30),70-S)+square(X=x*2%W,360+sin(X/99+y/9+t/y*150)/5*y+(noise(X/99+t/2,y))**5*99,sin(R/2)*(y/90+12))}
